%% Sequence 4 - Use case: Load the scanner page and browse the rule catalogue
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant UI as Browser
    participant API as FastAPI route
    participant FS as Static files
    participant REG as default_checks registry

    U->>UI: navigate to /
    UI->>API: GET /
    API->>FS: read index.html
    FS-->>API: file contents
    API-->>UI: 200 OK, HTML page

    par page initialisation
        UI->>API: GET /checks
        API->>REG: default_checks()
        REG-->>API: 14 Check objects
        API->>API: map each to CheckOut(name, weight)
        API-->>UI: 200 OK, 14 rules
        UI->>UI: show rule count in masthead
    and
        UI->>API: GET /scans
        API-->>UI: 200 OK, recent scans
        UI->>UI: fill history table
    end

    UI-->>U: page ready for input
